Victor Milenkovic, 5th MSI Worksh. Comp. Geom.
<p>
<LI><A HREF="http://docs.vircomnet.com/mobility/Shipbuilding_vc/fabricforsail.html">Cutting
fabric for sails</A>, Eugene Popov.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://ntc.tx.ncsu.edu/html/REPORTS/RESEARCH-FOLDER/part.html">Part Layout and Optimization of Part Shape</A>,
