National Textile Center.
<P>
<li><a href="ftp://ams.sunysb.edu/pub/geometry/msi-workshop/95/daniels.ps.gz">The Restrict/Evaluate/Subdivide Paradigm for Translational
Containment</a>,
Karen Daniels, 5th MSI Worksh. Comp. Geom.
<p>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.gmd.de/GMD/Institutes/SCAI/alg/nesting/nesting.html">Two dimensional cutting and packing problems in the textile and leather
manufacturing industry</A>, T. Lengauer, Inst. for Algorithms and
Scientific Computing, German Natl. Research Ctr. for Information
Technology.
